&lt;p&gt;We are delighted to offer the opportunity for a highly motivated and experienced paramedic clinical fellow to join our Banes, Wiltshire and Swindon (BSW) Primary Care Training Hub.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; The BSW Training hub is hosted by the CCG but employees will be employed by local GP Federation in B&amp;NES. The Training hub has a wide range of disciplines on the team but we are looking for a paramedic to join us. This role will work with GP practices that employ paramedics to advise them on good practice relating to induction, probation/preceptorship, competency framework, appraisal, peer support and continuing professional development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be required to lead the development of the role of the paramedic in primary care.&lt;/p&gt;
